<section class="py-16 px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-primary font-semibold mb-2">{{ section.settings.eyebrow }}</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
      {{ section.settings.content }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Story",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eyebrow",
      "label": "Eyebrow Text",
      "default": "OUR STORY"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "About Sloe Fit"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "id": "content",
      "label": "Content",
      "default": "<p>Sloe Fit was built to remove the stress and guesswork from training.</p><p>We saw too many lifters overwhelmed by conflicting advice, complicated protocols, and supplement companies making empty promises. So we created a system that's clean, disciplined, and actually works.</p><p>Our supplements are formulated with transparent ingredients at clinical doses. No proprietary blends. No inflated claims. Just what you need to support your training.</p><p>The Sloe Fit app connects your supplements to your workouts, giving you a complete performance system. Beginners get simple, guided plans they can trust. Serious lifters get the tools to plan sessions, track progress, and stay locked in without overthinking.</p><p>We're not here to sell you miracles. We're here to help you build strength, stay consistent, and get results that last.</p>"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "About Story"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}

